<div class="text-container">
    <div class="text-center">
        <p>When I was 12 my older brother gave me an acoustic guitar. He taught me some basic chords and a couple songs. I played off and on until my junior year of high school when I decided I wanted to learn how to sing and play guitar. It became my obsession. I would spend hours in my basement learning new songs and practicing my skills on the guitar. </p>
    </div>
</div>

