<div class="text-container">
    <div class="text-center">
        <p>After my mission I decided I wanted to get better at electric guitar and to join a band. I bought a bass guitar and a new electric guitar with two amps. This was a wonderful decision. I spent that summer recording myself playing all the parts to some of my favorite songs. When I came back to school I met some guys who were starting a pop punk band, and I decided to join their band. I spent about a year in Peaked in High School and also helped out playing bass for a band called Dead in The Neighbors Pool. </p>
    </div>
</div>
