<div class="text-container">
    <div class="text-center">
        <p>As hard as it is to believe I am not an avid punk music guy. I like it, but its not my favorite. Hence, My Other Band (MoB) was born. We play Alternative/Indie music. We have spent the last few months writing music and are getting close to releasing an EP and touring. I love Music. It is how I best express myself. When I am making music or performing, I feel completely alive. I want to be able to share my love and knowledge of music with as many people as possible.</p>
